name: Jumping Over It with Nathaniel Bandy
overview:
Why did I make this? This horrible climb up an impossible mountain. I would have made something you would have liked... A game that was fulfilling. That would save your progress and handhold you steadily forward. Since success is delicious, that could have been fun. Instead, I must confess, this isn't fun. It tastes of bitterness; it's capricious. It probably has gay baby jails. It lacks lenience. It's bracing inhumane, but not everyone's the same. I created this game for a certain kind of person. To hurt them.

Narration by Nathaniel Bandy

Don't play this, unless you want to be hurt.

(Yes, this game is a meme)
